</p>
<p>Phew! We spent time on these because these are the mistakes and errors that we <em>all</em>
make when starting with namespaces. They're annoying, unless you can debug them quickly.
If you're ever not sure about a "Class Not Found" error, the problem is almost always
a missing <code>use</code> statement.</p>
<p>Update the other spots that reference <code>PDO</code>:</p>
